Datensatzklasse VulkanInstance.QueueFamily

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
Kartoffel.Licht.Vulkan.VulkanInstance.QueueFamily
Datensatzkomponenten:
flags - the flags of this Queuefamily
flags_hasGB - true if VK10.VK_QUEUE_GRAPHICS_BIT is set in flags
flags_hasCB - true if VK10.VK_QUEUE_COMPUTE_BIT is set in flags
flags_hasTB - true if VK10.VK_QUEUE_TRANSFER_BIT is set in flags
flags_hasSB - true if VK10.VK_QUEUE_SPARSE_BINDING_BIT is set in flags
flags_hasPB - true if VK11.VK_QUEUE_PROTECTED_BIT is set in flags
maxQueueCount - the amount of queues this family has
timestampValidBits - timestampValidBits
Umschließende Klasse:
VulkanInstance
public static record VulkanInstance.QueueFamily(int flags, boolean flags_hasGB, boolean flags_hasCB, boolean flags_hasTB, boolean flags_hasSB, boolean flags_hasPB, int maxQueueCount, int timestampValidBits) extends Record
A QueueFamily, of which Queues can be created. All Queues of this family have the same properties.
